316
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,160
Demi kamu, Yan Xun

317
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:37,960
berulang kali mengabaikan Negara Yanbei.

318
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,160
Jika kamu tidak mati,

319
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,800
dendam rakyat Negara Yanbei

320
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,510
dan dendam Yan Xun

321
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:45,750
tidak akan pernah terbalaskan selamanya.

322
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:50,680
Teruslah hidup.

323
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:57,160
Zhong Yu!

324
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:18,680
Nona Yu.

325
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,350
Nona Yu.

326
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:24,350
Zhong Yu.

327
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:27,640
Zhong Yu, di mana kamu?

328
00:27:28,310 --> 00:27:29,920
Zhong Yu.

329
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:44,240
Jenderal,

330
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,590
