351
00:28:14,830 --> 00:28:16,070
Lalu, siapa yang tahu?

352
00:28:16,070 --> 00:28:16,680
Tuan, Nona.

353
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,740
Mi Anda sudah siap.

354
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,350
Masih ada dua hari.

355
00:28:22,350 --> 00:28:24,080
Aku akan kembali dua hari lagi.

356
00:28:28,120 --> 00:28:28,800
Ikuti dia.

357
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:29,350
Baik.

358
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,160
Kasihanilah aku.

359
00:28:45,510 --> 00:28:46,720
Kasihanilah aku.

360
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:47,880
Beri aku sedikit makanan.

361
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,110
Kasihanilah aku.

362
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,720
Semuanya dengarkan aku baik-baik.

363
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,590
Mulai hari ini,

364
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:54,240
